{"type": "article", "id": 13008, "title": "你骑车的时候都穿什么？有他们这么美吗？", "description": "英国版自行车着装时尚指南，你可能也用得到。\r\n", "date": "2015-08-05T08:41:31Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 13938, "name": "单车时尚"}], "category": 19, "author": 399912, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 156, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702122759hU5wTMs6tyBizSWY.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"background-color:#F9F9F9;\">据说有一年的巴黎时装周，张曼玉骑了个单车就跑去看秀了。为此，那些穿着华丽衣服和高跟鞋，挤到巴黎走红毯看秀的女明星们受了点“惊吓”。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"background-color:#F9F9F9;\">单车早就不是交通工具的代名词了。在城市中，单车出行也是一种生活态度的表达。<span style=\"text-align:start;background-color:#F9F9F9;\">尤其在现在的时装周上，时尚潮人都爱骑着单车<span style=\"text-align:start;background-color:#F9F9F9;\">翩翩出行。</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/fashion/people/stylish-celebrity-cyclists/kelly-bensimon/\" target=\"_blank\">最近，英国的《每日电讯报》就集合了各路明星和模特的单车时尚造型。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"background-color:#F9F9F9;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016070212274810gpTu5qy4VhtGDk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"background-color:#F9F9F9;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122748waX1PShOs43yMuBT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"background-color:#F9F9F9;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122749k80OL97lNrvCItqd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.60052219\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"background-color:#F9F9F9;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122750qInkpYJtjCUlrG4Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.60092593\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"background-color:#F9F9F9;\">其实，单车时尚已深入人心，高手在民间。现在有两个很火的以单车为主题的博客。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"background-color:#F9F9F9;\"><span>丹麦记者、电影导演兼摄影师 Mikael Colville-Andersen 做了一个 <span style=\"text-align:start;background-color:#F9F9F9;\">Cycle Chic 的博客。</span></span></span><span style=\"background-color:#F9F9F9;\">Colville-Andersen 爱好拍摄哥本哈根街头骑自行车的时髦男女。2007 年 6 月，在积累了相当数量的自行车时髦街拍照片后，他创立了这个街拍博客</span><span style=\"background-color:#F9F9F9;\">。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"background-color:#F9F9F9;\"><a href=\"http://www.copenhagencyclechic.com\" target=\"_blank\">有兴趣的可以点击这里。</a></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"background-color:#F9F9F9;\">现在模仿 <span style=\"text-align:start;background-color:#F9F9F9;\">Cycle Chic 的还有另外一个博客叫<a href=\"http://www.bikepretty.com\" target=\"_blank\"> Bike Pretty </a></span><a href=\"http://www.bikepretty.com\" target=\"_blank\"> </a>，博主模仿了<span style=\"text-align:start;background-color:#F9F9F9;\"> </span><span style=\"text-align:start;background-color:#F9F9F9;\">Cycle Chic 的街拍拍摄手法找到了许多来自大街小巷的漂亮单车以及漂亮的人。</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"background-color:#F9F9F9;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122751xK7J5YlWD0UzyEPH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"background-color:#F9F9F9;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122751xNAdQyh4utKXDI6B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"background-color:#F9F9F9;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"background-color:#F9F9F9;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122752z7BQgAJZ5fDMm2bS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"background-color:#F9F9F9;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122752gXFc6hVjsUoLY0kP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"background-color:#F9F9F9;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122753JmcxvwXdPbGNh8DO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122754o951vPyC7X4KFpqT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122754zkueArTW6OUJhB3K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.525\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"background-color:#F9F9F9;\"><span style=\"text-align:start;background-color:#F9F9F9;\">在好打扮的英国，每年都会举行复古自行车赛。</span>今年，4 月18 日，<span style=\"background-color:#F8F8F8;\"> The Tweed Run（奔跑吧，花呢外套）在伦敦</span>开赛。但这个比赛的重点跟环法比赛不一样，<span style=\"background-color:#F8F8F8;\">The Tweed Run 要求的不是速度和力量，而是潇洒和美感。比赛只要求参赛者必须穿着代表英伦经典的粗花呢单品出行，男女不限，老少皆宜。</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"background-color:#F9F9F9;\"><span style=\"background-color:#F8F8F8;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122755ed0pXzmTuMHrOLQx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122755zjxEp1bPsiUhBu0e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122756B3z4imeVSEqostCX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.9537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122756aEvoO19L46RKicPg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"background-color:#F9F9F9;\"><span style=\"background-color:#F8F8F8;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021227576B1gbM9Pfx70HOpk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.45833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"background-color:#F9F9F9;\"><span style=\"background-color:#F8F8F8;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122757h1XzOURka5r4vVGx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.77314815\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"background-color:#F9F9F9;\"><span style=\"background-color:#F8F8F8;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122758BPcgHvWzwedbijNY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8962963\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n"}